  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttachmentInfo
    Used to store attachment information.
    AttachmentServlet
    This servlet gets the input stream for a given msg part and pushes it out to the browser with the correct content type.
    FilterServlet
    This servlet is used to determine whether the user is logged in before forwarding the request to the selected URL.
    ListAttachmentsTag
    Custom tag for listing message attachments.
    ListAttachmentsTEI
    Extra information class to support the scripting variable created by the ListAttachmentsTag class.
    ListMessagesTag
    Custom tag for listing messages.
    ListMessagesTEI
    Extra information class to support the scripting variable created by the ListMessagesTag class.
    MailUserBean
    This JavaBean is used to store mail user information.
    MessageInfo
    Used to store message information.
    MessageTag
    Custom tag for retrieving a message.
    MessageTEI
    Extra information class to support the scripting variable created by the MessagesTag class.
    SendTag
    Custom tag for sending messages.
